verbose_text: In the sequential fragmentation from Cu (II) 8 (HCO 2) 17 - towards Cu (II) 2 (HCO 2) 5 - and Cu (II) (HCO 2) 3 -, stoichiometric dicopper tetraformate molecules Cu (II) 2 (HCO 2) 4 are lost preferentially, reaction (1), but loss of copper diformate Cu (II) (HCO 2) 2 is also observed, reaction (2).
